<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 36.1 (October 7, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The price of this item has been increased to 2700, up from 2630.</li><li>Haste has been reduced to 40, down from 45.</li><li>The cooldown reduction component of the Netherbind passive will now only trigger against the primary target so that Fate will no longer reduce its cooldown.</li><li>The cooldown of the Netherbind passive has been increased to 15, up from 10.</li><li>The Netherbind passive now has diminishing returns when applied in rapid succession. Attempting to root a target with Netherbind that has been affected by a previous Netherbind within the last 5 seconds will result in the root duration being reduced to 50% of the previous root's duration.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28 (April 8, 2014)</h4><ul><li>The Netherbind passive ability will now only trigger on your primary target.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Haste reduced to 45, down from 55.</li><li>The root duration of this item's passive ability has been increased to 1 seconds, up from 0.5.</li><li>The cooldown of this item's passive ability has been reduced to 10 seconds, down from 15.</li><li>Price reduced to 2630, down from 2865.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4>New Item<ul><li>This new item grants 55 Haste and is built from Clarity.</li><li>The Netherbind passive ability has been moved to this new item, and removed from Insight.</li></ul>